FRONTS AFFECTING THE UK WITH A RIDGE IN THE EERN ATLANTIC AHEAD OF A NUMBER
OF LOW PRESSURE SYSTEMS. DURING SUNDAY A WEAK RIDGE WILL MOV ACROSS THE S
